      <title>新加坡风险投资公司在估值低迷的情况下筹集初创企业债务基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/singapore-vc-raises-startup-debt-fund-amid-depressed-valuations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Genesis Alternative Ventures 是一家为初创企业和成长期公司提供贷款的私人贷款机构，由于全球投资者对东南亚的初创企业行业仍持谨慎态度，该机构以低于目标的价格完成了第二只债务基金的募集。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-10/singapore-vc-raises-startup-debt-fund-amid-depressed-valuations</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Sep 2024 01:58:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
